```plantuml
@startuml MyEMS_myems

package "MyEMS Energy Management System" {

    [Web Browser] as Browser
    [Mobile App] as Mobile

    package "Frontend" {
        [Admin UI] as AdminUI
        [User UI] as UserUI
    }

    package "API Layer" {
        [Falcon REST API] as API
    }

    package "Business Logic" {
        [Data Acquisition] as DataAcquisition
        [Data Cleaning] as DataCleaning
        [Normalization] as Normalization
        [Aggregation] as Aggregation
        [Reporting] as Reporting
        [Fault Detection] as FaultDetection
        [Billing] as Billing
        [User Management] as UserManagement
    }

    package "Data Storage" {
        [System DB] as SystemDB
        [Energy DB] as EnergyDB
        [Billing DB] as BillingDB
        [Historical DB] as HistoricalDB
        [Carbon DB] as CarbonDB
    }

    package "External Systems" {
        [IoT Devices] as IoT
        [Modbus TCP] as Modbus
        [Email/SMS] as Notification
        [WeChat] as WeChat
    }
}

Browser --> AdminUI : HTTP/HTTPS
Browser --> UserUI : HTTP/HTTPS
Mobile --> UserUI : HTTP/HTTPS

AdminUI --> API : REST/JSON
UserUI --> API : REST/JSON

API --> DataAcquisition
API --> DataCleaning
API --> Normalization
API --> Aggregation
API --> Reporting
API --> FaultDetection
API --> Billing
API --> UserManagement

DataAcquisition --> IoT : MQTT
DataAcquisition --> Modbus : Modbus TCP

DataCleaning --> EnergyDB
Normalization --> EnergyDB
Aggregation --> EnergyDB
Aggregation --> HistoricalDB
Reporting --> EnergyDB
Reporting --> HistoricalDB
Reporting --> CarbonDB
Billing --> BillingDB
Billing --> EnergyDB
UserManagement --> SystemDB

FaultDetection --> Notification
FaultDetection --> WeChat

@enduml
```